data.description: Honey, Stop the Car! Look it’s an incredible 3 story townhouse with 3 Master Suites - A true gem! Don't miss this fantastic opportunity to reside in an end-unit townhouse perfectly situated in the highly desirable swim/tennis community of Sugar Hill. The chef's kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, stained cabinets, a built-in microwave, an electric stove, a new oven, and ample space for entertainment. You'll have a clear view of the family room with a cozy fireplace from the kitchen. Enjoy the luxury of three primary suites, each with spacious bedrooms, walk-in closets, private bathrooms featuring double vanities, and separate shower and tub. A generous loft area is perfect for a home office, study, or additional living space. Large windows flood the space with natural light. The private deck provides a picturesque overlook of the meticulously manicured golf course. FHA approved.  100% Financing Available.
